SAMPLE GAMES DISCLAIMER

The game implementations included in this repository (located in the "games/"
directory) are independent, original works created solely as sample
demonstrations of the game-console platform. They are provided for
educational and personal, non-commercial use.

These sample games implement generic, unprotectable game mechanics (such as
bouncing a ball between paddles, or shooting at descending rows of enemies)
that have existed in the public domain of game design for decades. They are
not copies, ports, adaptations, or derivative works of any specific commercial
video game product.

No proprietary source code, game assets, trade dress, character designs,
audiovisual elements, or trademarks belonging to any third party have been
used in the creation of these samples. Any similarity to existing commercial
games is attributable solely to the use of common, generic game design
patterns and mechanics.

The names used for these sample games within this repository (e.g., "Pong",
"Space Invaders") are used descriptively to identify the genre of gameplay
demonstrated. If any such name constitutes a trademark of a third party, its
use here is purely descriptive and nominative, and no sponsorship, affiliation,
or endorsement by the trademark holder is implied.

THE SAMPLE GAMES ARE PROVIDED "AS IS" WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND. THE
AUTHOR ASSUMES NO LIABILITY FOR ANY CLAIMS ARISING FROM THE USE OR
DISTRIBUTION OF THESE SAMPLES.
